properties.description:
XLSX generation from a XSL and publish to the /var/www/html/ directory of the remote server

Need a remote linux endpoint and the following script execute remotely

# Importing pandas
import pandas as pd
import sys
# The webpage URL whose table we want to extract
url = "http://127.0.0.1/"
url = url+sys.argv[1]

# Assign the table data to a Pandas dataframe
table = pd.read_html(url)[0]

# Store the dataframe in Excel file
ext = ".xlsx"
out = sys.argv[1]+ext
table.to_excel(out)
